---
import { site } from "../data/site";
import Icon from "./ui/Icon.astro";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative border-t border-white/5 bg-ink-950 py-14">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <a href="#top" class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-ink-900 ring-1 ring-brass-500/40">
            <Icon name="droplets" class="h-5 w-5 text-brass-300" />
          </span>
          <span class="leading-tight">
            <span class="block font-display font-bold text-white">{site.shortName}</span>
            <span class="block text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brass-300">с заботой о вашем авто</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-white/55 max-w-xs">
          Ручная мойка, химчистка, полировка и детейлинг у м. Коломенская.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/40">Контакты</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href={site.phone.href} class="text-white hover:text-brass-200">
              {site.phone.display}
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-white/65">{site.address.line1}, {site.address.line2}</li>
          <li class="text-white/65">{site.address.city}</li>
          <li class="text-white/65">{site.hoursShort}</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2">
          <a href={site.whatsapp} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="WhatsApp" class="grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white/70 transition-colors hover:border-brass-400 hover:text-brass-200">
            <Icon name="message-circle" class="h-4 w-4" />
          </a>
          <a href={site.telegram} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Telegram" class="grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white/70 transition-colors hover:border-brass-400 hover:text-brass-200">
            <Icon name="send" class="h-4 w-4" />
          </a>
          <a href={site.yandexCard} target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Яндекс.Карты" class="grid h-9 w-9 place-items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white/70 transition-colors hover:border-brass-400 hover:text-brass-200">
            <Icon name="map-pin" class="h-4 w-4" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/40">Меню</div>
        <ul class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#advantages" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brass-200">Преимущества</a></li>
          <li><a href="#services" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brass-200">Услуги</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brass-200">О нас</a></li>
          <li><a href="#reviews" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brass-200">Отзывы</a></li>
          <li><a href="#map" class="text-white/70 hover:text-brass-200">Контакты</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-10 border-white/5" />

    <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-white/40 md:flex-row md:items-center">
      <div>© {year} {site.shortName}. Все права защищены.</div>
      <div class="max-w-xl text-white/40">
        Сайт носит информационный характер и не собирает персональные данные пользователей. Цены не являются публичной офертой.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
